  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >--- ​<strong>​Roguelike Mode, Now Available!​</strong>​ ---</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ancient monsters are invading the castle—join the fight and defend against the dragon’s assault!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Mix and match equipment for diverse combat styles!<br>• Summon divine guardians to fight by your side!<br>• Unlock 20+ new achievements—take on the challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/a7200c765b672b5d62f008a494543d26.avif?t=1753154782\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras_big/a7200c765b672b5d62f008a494543d26.avif?t=1753154782 width=1600 height=900 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>--- ​​Identity Deduction Mode​​ ---</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Castle of Mist\" draws inspiration from social deduction games like Werewolf, featuring first-person immersive castle exploration. Players engage in psychological battles within the mysterious castle, influencing the game's outcome by searching for items and triggering hidden events. With suspenseful execution phases and multiple random events, each round delivers a uniquely thrilling experience!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Identity Deduction × Multiplayer Online × Intense Social Deception  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travelers from around the world have stumbled into a rift in time and space, trapped in an abandoned castle haunted by malevolent spirits and their curses. To escape, they must break the curse—but dark forces lurk in the shadows. Will they work together to survive, or betray each other for victory?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  Faction Warfare: A Battle of Lies and Truth  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Randomly assigned as Righteous or Hidden Evil, compete for victory through tasks, votes, and sabotage.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The Righteous must restore energy and complete tasks, while the Evil sabotage in secret—even disguising themselves as allies!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >High-Stakes Exploration: Strategy Decides Survival  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Scavenge for parts, fight for special items (like runestones to disrupt votes), or hunt for the Contract—a deadly chance to win alone!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Energy towers, crosses, broken components… Every choice could turn the tide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Psychological Warfare: Who Will Outlast the Rest?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Vote, debate, frame—use words and acting to earn trust… or orchestrate a fatal betrayal.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• If half the tasks fail, the Evil unleash a massacre! The Righteous must expose the traitors, or face total annihilation.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cooperate? Or betray?—The last one standing isn’t always the winner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/2fd777d6a267ada09d197068f4dbb8bc.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/2fd777d6a267ada09d197068f4dbb8bc.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/2fd777d6a267ada09d197068f4dbb8bc.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/0541c82e0c089e708d2048d2e593c100.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/0541c82e0c089e708d2048d2e593c100.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/0541c82e0c089e708d2048d2e593c100.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/94c03884dd078e88716190ec85f33763.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/94c03884dd078e88716190ec85f33763.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/94c03884dd078e88716190ec85f33763.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/4b488f75e1d49611d120d52e5bb0c171.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/4b488f75e1d49611d120d52e5bb0c171.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/4b488f75e1d49611d120d52e5bb0c171.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/0c00a14b007b69cb9c09599f0b23b3ed.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/0c00a14b007b69cb9c09599f0b23b3ed.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/0c00a14b007b69cb9c09599f0b23b3ed.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/872b3afc1b6c9c3f8d5fdb33eb3a13c3.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/872b3afc1b6c9c3f8d5fdb33eb3a13c3.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/872b3afc1b6c9c3f8d5fdb33eb3a13c3.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/1a579358559bcbf09ea6c707d10912c8.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/1a579358559bcbf09ea6c707d10912c8.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/1a579358559bcbf09ea6c707d10912c8.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/b5706c23efb7c95281a5fbc03c068e7c.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it