gh tasks, votes, and sabotage.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The Righteous must restore energy and complete tasks, while the Evil sabotage in secret—even disguising themselves as allies!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >High-Stakes Exploration: Strategy Decides Survival  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Scavenge for parts, fight for special items (like runestones to disrupt votes), or hunt for the Contract—a deadly chance to win alone!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Energy towers, crosses, broken components… Every choice could turn the tide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Psychological Warfare: Who Will Outlast the Rest?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Vote, debate, frame—use words and acting to earn trust… or orchestrate a fatal betrayal.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• If half the tasks fail, the Evil unleash a massacre! The Righteous must expose the traitors, or face total annihilation.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cooperate? Or betray?—The last one standing isn’t always the winner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/2fd777d6a267ada09d197068f4dbb8bc.poster.avif?t=1753154782\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/2fd777d6a267ada09d197068f4dbb8bc.webm?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/2fd777d6a267ada09d197068f4dbb8bc.mp4?t=1753154782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505060/extras/0541c82e0c089e708d2048d2e593c100.poster.avif?t=1